{"type": "article", "id": 22643, "title": "在西班牙的这家幼儿园里，有迷你假山和巨型象棋", "description": "幼儿园有点意思，后面的展览更有趣。", "date": "2016-02-23T07:00:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4187, "name": "幼儿园"}, {"id": 5133, "name": "西班牙"}, {"id": 5248, "name": "国际象棋"}, {"id": 23761, "name": "Rosan Bosch Studio"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071854284Lf09uyOXIdwGZ85.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>最近，哥本哈根的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.rosanbosch.com\">Rosan Bosch Studio</a> 设计了一个幼儿园，在这个幼儿园里，有<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/02/21/this-spanish-kindergarten-is-filled-with-mountains-caves-and-chess/\">假山、有岩洞，还有小孩儿身体那么大的</a>棋子，供孩子们在小王国里玩乐。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071854164zeLEjRrNXk7GQhP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这就是名叫 LICEO EUROPA 的幼儿园了</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185416BbthEDXyHvIl4JGZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">“景观峡谷”、“沙丘”、沙漠与柔性材料组合在一起，形成了一个非正式的学习空间</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185417DJGvgUFtw5pzjWfO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">假山可供小孩子们玩耍和穿梭</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185417D7kLBUtsGz8cI6wQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185418zNr0UAd8JqaVxIXb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185418GDymS9v3XOorxZuf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">和人身一样大的棋子</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185419YAVm8uvHcxTyDOPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是一个供老师和孩子们互动的空间</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185419FHNEClkuBXAa6ib1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p>除了这个 LICEO EUROPA ，<a href=\"http://www.rosanbosch.com\">Rosan Bosch Studio</a> 还设计过不少类似的空间，比如这个位于迪拜的幼儿园——<a href=\"http://www.rosanbosch.com/en/project/sheikh-zayed-academy\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Sheikh Zayed Academy for Boys</a>。该项目已动工，以下是概念图：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185420xUyzh1fgrTtSOMPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185420BlHOe4iZ3h7xUpws.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185421vUBI2MATsV3lf4Zx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185421GjT61DiOBrFYq42x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p>以下是 <a href=\"http://www.rosanbosch.com\">Rosan Bosch Studio</a> 完成的其他设计：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071854220t9qOwKoTzHB2QUp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Steno Museum 的展览，名叫 \"Darling Body, Difficult Body\"，这个展览空间探索的是男女性的身体</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071854228K4fbluDnhLkVg3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">展览现场</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185423Xtn6KaMgTz70yE1G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718542357OxNEPn2TVyd9Ag.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">女厕中的装饰</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185424sb6RDBY15zErqyl7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">男女厕所</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185424ugminXBGlER7tCk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">玩具身体</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185425Yv7XyRu0txlaHoGD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">展览现场</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185425GT8m2yEKfz3M54S0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68350669\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">University College Nordjylland，这是 Rosan Bosch Studio 的另一处作品，红色的“树杈”很显眼</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071854268sPeVDBd3AIuTyp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185427PUi6zAYadGx5b7eX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> Rosan Bosch Studio 设计的乐高空间</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185427z5S1rWi0R2JYhw9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185428ngLofrdWGKuEyOxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68554396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">乐高空间</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185428ehnBk3rVAj7mT2iQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6618705\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/02/21/this-spanish-kindergarten-is-filled-with-mountains-caves-and-chess/\">contemporist</a></p>\n\n\n"}